{"tid":718370,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無邊次扑野經歷你係最撚深刻","createTime":"2018-06-26T17:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T23:10:31.000Z","uid":54581,"like":47,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e2178dc1270c772df45962ab0ae742a6a13317","tid":718370,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"第一次破處/中出 依啲我反而覺得無乜特別<br />\n<br />\n最撚深刻反而係有次ex幫我含<br />\n<br />\n但奈何佢個口太細 含左一少半碌鳩已經到頂 再深啲真係屌喉嚨<br />\n<br />\n咁岩個時睇av上腦，想試下深喉，就叫佢慢慢含深啲 我又用啲力禁住佢個頭頂上去<br />\n<br />\n入左大半個陣佢個頭一抽起 就嘔落我碌鳩到。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個時真係呆撚左 我諗緊係咪我碌鳩太臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後沖完涼 我扮下嬲 佢又臉都紅埋tum番我話我想點都得<br />\n<br />\n咁我就順水推舟，真係黎個深喉，不過幾下之後佢又咳又流眼水 啲口水絲流到成個胸都係<br />\n見到我都唔忍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係69個時奶番佢春袋同啜下粒蛋當無數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fd2c92894caa11a3749d89026a6b15d4f64fc0","tid":718370,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"M到屌閪<br />\n<br />\n搞到成地血"},{"pid":"c0482375525bc98ad0dae04e9ff50a044edabd73","tid":718370,"uid":157834,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:45:09.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6a8578346100038cde2e9704b316aa29acf4b3","tid":718370,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6fd2c92894caa11a3749d89026a6b15d4f64fc0","tid":718370,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"M到屌閪<br />\n<br />\n搞到成地血"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T17:45:38.000Z","msg":"無搵毛巾墊住？<br />\n<br />\n同埋好撚臭喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔帶套真係唔敢插入去"},{"pid":"fa1a0490ac8fbb0f345e5fe5580c41fee05390b1","tid":718370,"uid":188